<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="present-adj">present <strong><em>adj</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'preznt/    美 /'preznt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>现在的；如今的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the present</strong> difficulties / problems / <strong>situation</strong> 
当前的困难/问题/形势</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>At the present time</strong> we have no explanation for this.
目前我们对此不作任何解释。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>在场的；出席的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All students are required to be <strong>present at</strong> the school meeting.
所有学生务必出席全校大会。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Everybody present welcomed the decision. 
在场的所有人都对这个决定表示欢迎。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>presently /'prezntli/ adv   </p></div>